_sText:
This has all stock textures and sprites so it will easily run on server
with no extra crap.   I don't know if you could use it on a Gun Game server.
It is set up like a normal death match.   If you want to mod it to run on Gun Game server then fine.  Like I said,  I don't have any idea what the difference in the programming for gun game would be,  if any.  

This was the final version of the map,  or test map package that I put up.
chupong2sky5fix2  was about the name in it.  Golden trees was a add on package that I had a hell of a time making work when I reinstalled game.
So I erased them and made it all stock!!
